These instructions differ somewhat from the instructions in the
original package, as the Debian distribution includes libsciplot.so as
a shared library.

To compile these examples:

 cd /tmp
 e=/usr/share/doc/sciplot-dev/examples
 make VPATH=$e LOADLIBES=-lsciplot CFLAGS='-Wall -O2' xyplot realtime

and you can run one with:

 ./xyplot < /usr/share/doc/sciplot-dev/examples/data.txt
